{"tid":440865,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大魁北克通過法案　用政府服務時禁遮臉","createTime":"2017-10-19T07:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T07:30:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"879a6fa790e4bbc2ae2eed6156ffc05ae770f3c3","tid":440865,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171019/s00005/00850953e758929f00cf13c31b13a34f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171019%2Fs00005%2F00850953e758929f00cf13c31b13a34f.jpg&h=97a17af6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大魁北克省通過「宗教中立」法案，禁止公眾使用政府及公共服務時，以面紗等遮擋臉容。魁北克當局指法案並非針對穆斯林，但評論指這仍會令穆斯林女性被邊緣化。有法律專家預料法案會被入稟挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n被稱為「第62條」（Bill 62）的「宗教中立」法案於當地時間周三（18日），在魁北克省議會以66對51票通過。除規定公務員、警察、教師、巴士司機，及在公營醫院及健康中心工作的醫生、助產士和牙醫不可遮臉外，民眾使用公共交通及市政服務，包括進入圖書館、上學和看病時，同樣不可以面紗等遮臉。戴面紗的女性可申請「處所」，讓她們遮着臉部使用政府服務，但涉及保安或辨認身分等原因時，申請可被拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n魁北克省政府表示，法案針對所有種類的面紗或面罩，稱並非針對穆斯林。加拿大一間調查公司2016年數據顯示，加拿大共有約6%穆斯林女性會穿著只露出眼睛的全臉面紗（niqab）或露出臉孔的包頭長袍（chador）。有評論認為禁止穆斯林女性使用政府服務或任職政府工時遮臉，會令她們被邊緣化；法律專家則預計法案會被入稟挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n「第62條」法案同時停止省資助的兒童照顧服務提供宗教教育。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171019/s00005/1508393397291\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171019%2Fs00005%2F1508393397291&d=PtFwCEnN4a7PJ%2F0UQYE76BxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=69c17d05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171019%2Fs00005%2F1508393397291&h=7e3388a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171019/s00005/1508393397291</a>"},{"pid":"35ccf7bba90529bf3fe9b08e2b1039b350c92384","tid":440865,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"醫生連口罩都唔戴得?"},{"pid":"853c2c79d6576217c2fa2bbc7bbc67b49852e4cd","tid":440865,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:18:05.000Z","msg":"歐洲同美國ge今晚打老虎專區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f7784b546e9cff8af1e1fbf798d72d53a015d8","tid":440865,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"穆斯林唔融入你就做乜都冇用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊緣化，你遲下就真係邊緣化喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7606b4ca52ce2f6427ad645ef97c55017dc32c","tid":440865,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿拉狗神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}